{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"focus","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element/focus_event","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>focus 事件在元素获取焦点时触发。这个事件和&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/focusin_event\"><code>focusin</code></a>&nbsp;最大的区别仅仅在于后者会事件冒泡。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"基本信息","title":"基本信息","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"规范\">规范</dt>\n <dd><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-3-Events/#event-type-focus\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM L3</a></dd>\n <dt id=\"接口\">接口</dt>\n <dd><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FocusEvent\"><code>FocusEvent</code></a></dd>\n <dt id=\"是否冒泡\">是否冒泡</dt>\n <dd>否</dd>\n <dt id=\"能否取消默认\">能否取消默认</dt>\n <dd>否</dd>\n <dt id=\"事件目标\">事件目标</dt>\n <dd>Element</dd>\n <dt id=\"默认行为\">默认行为</dt>\n <dd>无。</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\">注释：这里的接口是指 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a> prior to Gecko&nbsp;24 (Firefox 24 / Thunderbird 24 / SeaMonkey 2.21). (<a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=855741\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">bug&nbsp;855741</a>)</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Property</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Type</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Description</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>target</code> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></td>\n   <td>Event target (DOM element)</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>type</code> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a></td>\n   <td>The type of event.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>bubbles</code> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a></td>\n   <td>Whether the event normally bubbles or not.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>cancelable</code> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a></td>\n   <td>Whether the event is cancellable or not.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>relatedTarget</code> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a> (DOM element)</td>\n   <td>null</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"事件委托","title":"事件委托","isH3":false,"content":"<p>此事件有两个可以实现事件委托的方法 : 通过在支持的浏览器上使用&nbsp;<code>focusin</code> 事件 (除了 Firefox 之外的所有浏览器), 或者通过设置 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener\"><code>addEventListener</code></a>&nbsp;的参数\"useCapture\" 值为 true:</p>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Event delegation sample\" id=\"frame_event_delegation\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-CN/docs/Web/Events/blur/_sample_.event_delegation.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>\n\n<p>(Sample code from <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/blur_event\">blur (event)</a>)</p>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/uievents/#event-type-focus","title":"UI Events"}],"query":"api.Element.focus_event"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.Element.focus_event","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element/focus_event/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"相关事件","title":"相关事件","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/focus_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">focus (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/blur_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">blur (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/focusin_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">focusin (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/focusout_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">focusout (en-US)</a></code></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"基本信息","id":"基本信息"},{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"事件委托","id":"事件委托"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"相关事件","id":"相关事件"}],"summary":"focus 事件在元素获取焦点时触发。这个事件和 focusin 最大的区别仅仅在于后者会事件冒泡。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Element: focus event","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Element: focus イベント","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"focus","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/element/focus_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/element/focus_event/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element","title":"Element"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element/focus_event","title":"focus"}],"pageTitle":"focus - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}